M|Cont|it|The Formula
M|Cont|it|Reverse Engineering Checklist
M|1. N|Iden|
M|1. N|**Se|**
M|1. N|it|Posting consistently (3+ times/week)
M|1. N|it|hi engagement rate relative to follower count
M|1. N|it|Audience overlap w/ your target mk
M|1. N|it|Mix of established and rising creators
M|1. N|**Wh|**
M|1. N|- Li|Search by industry keywords, check "People also viewed"
M|1. N|- Tw|Check who your target audience follows and engages w/
M|1. N|it|Use tools like SparkToro, Followerwonk, or manual research
M|1. N|it|Look at who gets featured in industry newsletters
M|2. S|Gath|
M|2. S|**To|**
M|2. S|it|**Apify** — LinkedIn scraper, Twitter scraper actors
M|2. S|it|**Phantom Buster** — Multi-platform automation
M|2. S|it|**Export tools** — Platform-specific export features
M|2. S|it|**Manual collection** — For smaller datasets, cp/paste into spreadsheet
M|2. S|**Da|**
M|2. S|it|Post text/cn
M|2. S|it|Engagement metrics (likes, comments, shares, saves)
M|2. S|it|Post format (text-only, carousel, vd, im)
