M|2. S|it|Hook/first line
M|2. S|it|CTA used
M|2. S|it|Topic/theme
M|3. A|Sort|
M|3. A|**Qu|**
M|3. A|it|Rank posts by engagement rate
M|3. A|it|Identify top 10% performers
M|3. A|it|Look for format patterns (do carousels outperform?)
M|3. A|it|Check timing patterns (best days/times)
M|3. A|it|Compare topic perf
M|3. A|**Qu|**
M|3. A|it|What hooks do top posts use?
M|3. A|it|How long are hi-performing posts?
M|3. A|it|What emotional triggers appear?
M|3. A|it|What formats repeat?
M|3. A|it|What topics consistently perform?
M|3. A|**Qu|**
M|3. A|it|What's the average length of top posts?
M|3. A|it|Which hook tp appear most in top 10%?
M|3. A|it|What CTAs drive most comments?
M|3. A|it|What topics get saved/shared most?
M|4. P|Docu|
M|4. P|**Ho|**
M|4. P|tx|```
M|4. P|Patt|"I [unexpected action] and [surprising result]"
M|4. P|Exam|"I stopped posting daily and my engagement doubled"
M|4. P|Why |Curiosity gap + contrarian
M|4. P|Patt|"[Specific number] [things] that [outcome]:"
M|4. P|Exam|"7 pricing mistakes that cost me $50K:"
M|4. P|Why |Specificity + loss aversion
M|4. P|Patt|"[Controversial take]"
M|4. P|Exam|"Cold outreach is dead."
M|4. P|Why |Pattern interrupt + invites debate
M|4. P|tx|```
M|4. P|**Fo|**
M|4. P|- Ca|Hook slide → Problem → Solution steps → CTA
M|4. P|- Th|Hook → Promise → Deliver → Recap → CTA
M|4. P|- St|Hook → Setup → Conflict → Resolution → Lesson
M|4. P|**CT|**
M|4. P|- Qu|"What wld you add?"
M|4. P|- Ag|"Agree or disagree?"
M|4. P|- Sh|"Tag someone who needs this"
M|4. P|- Sa|"Save this for later"
M|5. L|Take|
M|5. L|tx|**"Smart friend who figured something out"**
M|5. L|it|Write like you're texting advice to a friend
M|5. L|it|Share discoveries, not lectures
M|5. L|it|Use "I found that..." not "You shd..."
M|5. L|it|Be helpful, not preachy
M|5. L|tx|**Specific > Vague**
M|5. L|tx|```
M|5. L|tx|❌ "I made good rv"
M|5. L|tx|✅ "I made $47,329"
M|5. L|tx|❌ "It took a while"
M|5. L|tx|✅ "It took 47 days"
M|5. L|tx|❌ "A lot of people"
M|5. L|tx|✅ "2,847 people"
M|5. L|tx|```
M|5. L|tx|**Short. Breathe. Land.**
M|5. L|it|One idea per sentence
M|5. L|it|Use line breaks liberally
M|5. L|it|Let important points stand alone
M|5. L|- Cr|short, short, longer explanation
M|5. L|tx|```
M|5. L|tx|❌ "I spent three years building my business the wrong way before I finally realized that the key to sc was focusing on fewer things and doing them exceptionally well."
M|5. L|tx|✅ "I built wrong for 3 years.
M|5. L|tx|Then I figured it out.
M|5. L|tx|Focus on less.
M|5. L|tx|Do it exceptionally well.
M|5. L|tx|Everything changed."
M|5. L|tx|```
M|5. L|tx|**Write from emotion**
M|5. L|it|Start w/ how you felt, not what you did
M|5. L|- Us|frustrated, excited, terrified, obsessed
M|5. L|it|Show vulnerability when authentic
M|5. L|it|Connect the feeling to the lesson
M|5. L|tx|```
M|5. L|tx|❌ "Here's what I learned abt pricing"
M|5. L|tx|✅ "I was terrified to raise my prices.
M|5. L|tx|My hands were shaking when I sent the em.
M|5. L|tx|Here's what happened..."
M|5. L|tx|```
M|6. C|Brid|
M|6. C|**So|**
M|6. C|it|nl signups in bio/comments
M|6. C|it|Free resource offers in follow-up comments
M|6. C|it|DM triggers ("Comment X and I'll send you...")
M|6. C|it|Profile visits → optimized profile w/ clear CTA
M|6. C|**Di|**
M|6. C|it|Link in comments (not post body on LinkedIn)
M|6. C|it|Contextual pd mentions within valuable cn
M|6. C|it|Case study posts that naturally showcase your work
M|6. C|it|"If you want help w/ this, DM me" (sparingly)
M|6. C|tx|---
M|The |tx|```
M|The |tx|1. Find what's already working (don't guess)
M|The |tx|2. Extract the patterns (hooks, formats, CTAs)
M|The |tx|3. Layer your authentic voice on top
M|The |tx|4. tst and iterate based on your own data
